Messages.Value: Thank you for calling. This is Harper Jackson. How may I assist you?

Yes, hi. My name is Sarah Johnson and I'm having issues with my tech. I was supposed to be in San Francisco for a conference but my flight was delayed due to weather conditions and now I can't access my online conference. I need to know how I can access the conference.
I'm sorry to hear that, Sarah. I can definitely assist you with that. Can you please provide me with your confirmation number and the name of the conference?
My confirmation code is ABC123 and the conference is the Global Business Conference.
Thank you, Sarah. I've located your registration and it looks like you should have received an email with a link to access the conference. Have you tried checking your email?
Yes, I checked my email but I can't find the link. This is ridiculous, I paid a lot of money for this conference and now I can't even access it.
I completely understand your frustration, Sarah. Let me check if I can find the link and send it to you.
Thank you, that would be great.
I was able to find the link and just sent it to your email. Please check your inbox and see if you received it.
Yes, I just received it. Thank you so much for your help, Harper.
You're very welcome, Sarah. Do you have any other questions or concerns?
No, that's all. Thank you again for your help.
It was my pleasure, Sarah. Have a great day!
